{"tid":1272112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"示威之餘抽少少時間關心同路人","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T09:46:42.000Z","uid":263484,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e346a9b4cafe8556386031d3dcda54ee99ee8a2","tid":1272112,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"勇武又好，和理非都好，麻煩咁多位，如果呢段時間身邊有朋友或網友曾經表達過有尋死念頭，覺得自己冇用、失敗、心淡、因家人和情侶間政見不同、對呢個社會冇能為力嘅人，請大家盡量抽啲時間佢留意下關心佢地，因為過埋今日，政府仍然企硬的話，呢一班人好容易又激起想尋死念頭。 佢地未必想搵社工，但朋友間一句關心說話可以救到一條人命。<br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f689349518d253af32cf89dd9ac681ca46dfd571","tid":1272112,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34272d6e0e5c0a076b4a3c2951cc2059d9e14773","tid":1272112,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d43bb4ea4fcc42ae52d417f765166964b1c30e","tid":1272112,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be836a43d75f94c4c572ca888e7230a4c51bd5a6","tid":1272112,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"自膠再推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}